{"id":"655ec65a-2a96-4aa0-9af0-96fa4af29742","name":"Great Furry-Human War","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">War</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">. War never changes</mark></span><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">.</mark></p><p><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(1, 1, 1); color: inherit;\">War</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(1, 1, 1); color: inherit;\"> </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(1, 1, 1); color: inherit;\">happens for various reasons. Greed. Hatred. Personal benefit. But this war? This </mark></em><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(1, 1, 1); color: inherit;\">war</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(1, 1, 1); color: inherit;\"> </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(1, 1, 1); color: inherit;\">was not for victory, but for the very right to exist as free or even living beings.</mark></em></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">In 2020, there was a war between humanity and furries</mark></em></span>.</p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">{{User}} - You can be whoever you want. </mark></p><p><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Context - You see the human base being attacked. You can be a human soldier, a furry soldier, or a civilian seeing an attack from a nearby town. You can be a spy, a general, a pilot, or even a janitor if you want to.</mark></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"7wx5Z66DET1H8HZtWTJGU.webp","creator":"The_Devil_In_I","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["📚 Fictional","🪢 Scenario","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🐺 Furry"],"chats":1047,"messages":30426,"created_at":"2025-08-01T13:32:06.987228+00:00"}